  "detailed_description": "DMT: Dream Dealer is a first person exploration game were you enter your dreams and start a long journey between worlds.<br />\r\nYou'll never know if what you see is real, or if you are in trance. <br />\r\nAn experimental game made to delight your sensory system. <br />\r\nSurreal game inspirate in titles like: The Stanley Parable, Dear Esther... were the principal objective is to show what mind isn't able to imagine.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe story is explained by inner thoughts that will guide you through your dreams. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nSometimes they will try to confuse and deceive you...",
  "about_the_game": "DMT: Dream Dealer is a first person exploration game were you enter your dreams and start a long journey between worlds.<br />\r\nYou'll never know if what you see is real, or if you are in trance. <br />\r\nAn experimental game made to delight your sensory system. <br />\r\nSurreal game inspirate in titles like: The Stanley Parable, Dear Esther... were the principal objective is to show what mind isn't able to imagine.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe story is explained by inner thoughts that will guide you through your dreams. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nSometimes they will try to confuse and deceive you...",
